---
const questions = [
  {
    id: 'faq-1',
    title: 'How do I know which plan is right for me?',
    answer:
      "Choosing the right plan depends on your financial goals and preferences. Our team is here to help you assess your needs and find the plan that best fits your objectives, whether it's saving for the future, accessing premium benefits, or managing your wealth.",
  },
  {
    id: 'faq-2',
    title: 'How can I upgrade, downgrade, or cancel my plan?',
    answer:
      "You can easily upgrade, downgrade, or cancel your plan by contacting our customer support team. We'll assist you promptly with any changes to ensure your banking experience meets your evolving needs.",
  },
  // {
  //   id: 'faq-3',
  //   title: "What does 'lifetime access' mean exactly?",
  //   answer:
  //     'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Culpa, voluptas ipsa quia excepturi, quibusdam natus exercitationem sapiente tempore labore voluptatem.',
  // },
  // {
